sensors.12V.description: The voltage supplied by the power supply unit on the 12V rail.

sensors.12VStandby.description: The voltage supplied by the power supply unit on the 12V standby rail. The standby rail powers the subset of components needed to remotely start the system.
sensors.12VStandby.notes: The sensor name is '12 V Standby', and the sensor ID is '05h'. The lower critical voltage is 10.685V, the lower non-recoverable voltage is 10.045V, the upper critical voltage is 13.885V, and the upper non-recoverable voltage is 14.481V.
